{"tid":729891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖) 大波熟女曬提子 兩皇一后玩推車","createTime":"2018-07-05T02:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T05:43:13.000Z","uid":6604,"like":71,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d9869c73a6835d5fe28917442125571c2657b55e","tid":729891,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180704/small/1530686973_6ca2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180704%2Fsmall%2F1530686973_6ca2.png&h=d4f34d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180704/small/1530686556_2046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180704%2Fsmall%2F1530686556_2046.jpg&h=4eafdf0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180704/small/1530686563_22ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180704%2Fsmall%2F1530686563_22ec.jpg&h=53fb316f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2016/0710/20160710012540635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2016%2F0710%2F20160710012540635.jpg&h=0fe3e6f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.e123.hk/newsfeed/20150228/_28gk005_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e123.hk%2Fnewsfeed%2F20150228%2F_28gk005_.jpg&h=23a8da87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬，今日下晝突然同兩名男黨友，包括「肥老闆」張華峰同黨主席盧偉國喺走廊表演「推車」，話要請記者食成10元一粒嘅提子。<br />\n<br />\n鼠王芬話，早前大台有套講果欄嘅電視劇，「我煲哂啊！因為我細個係喺果欄附近長大，我阿爺同埋我阿公都係喺嗰度開舖頭，做鐵嘅生意」，自爆套劇大結局後翌日，佢即刻去咗油麻地果欄掃咗大批水果，目的係想推動大家支持果欄行業，今日就買生果畀記者食。<br />\n<br />\n鼠王芬介紹生果時，多次強調佢買嘅日本香印提子好貴，要成10蚊一粒，透露今日成車水果，就用咗佢2,000幾蚊！盧偉國聽到，就話粒提子點貴重，「都唔及得美芬心意咁貴重&hellip;&hellip;」其後仲突然對住鼠王芬唱出「情與義&hellip;&hellip;值千金，係咪啊？」鼠王芬聽完就笑言，經民聯有盧偉國，真係好似「愛登士家庭」喎。"},{"pid":"324c33fae2c7fd307b6a495eba88063dd30fe3ad","tid":729891,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2208e29a151889d3f72e326005a24c051b207784","tid":729891,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"jed"},{"pid":"c6b887d4d7a924f3381e0ac0fff426404205847c","tid":729891,"uid":65123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f14565a28d9d5c77573d500b2941a3c5f3f6c0e","tid":729891,"uid":188882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"同老鼠人獸交"},{"pid":"016e220d91115ef8c499a2d52398f07388525eb4","tid":729891,"uid":113234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"圖文相符 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe0c9b19d698c7af3bf86f5ca46f31fb53973ac","tid":729891,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"圖片與標題符合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82600114271bb77bce8dacbda6105a53bed95e21","tid":729891,"uid":20372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"我認我鹹濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3af23703686b6e9bf36bd811829ce477df293c","tid":729891,"uid":47209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"點解我會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset